data.description: Immaculately maintained two-story home situated in the Carmona Hills community convenient to Loop 410, Lackland Airforce Base and plenty of shopping and dining. The main level boasts an open layout with wood-like laminate flooring throughout, a secondary bedroom, a charming study and an abundance of natural light. The beautiful island kitchen features quartz countertops, black appliances, recessed lighting and opens to the spacious family room - perfect for entertaining. Upstairs includes a bonus family room/game room, two additional bedrooms and an over-sized primary suite with a full bath and a large walk-in closet. Outdoors, enjoy a charming covered patio area, full privacy fence and room to create your own outdoor oasis!
